Sometimes i caught myself doing crazy things i never thought i would do . *sigh #wavybrows #squigglebrows #crazybrows #sorrybrows A post shared by Khin Chan Myae Nyein (@khinchanmyae_nyein) on Sep 7, 2017 at 12:13pm PDT Separate the egg yolk from the white. Beat the yolk till the consistency is smooth. Apply to your eyebrows using a Q-tip or a brush. Keep it on for 20 minutes and rinse with warm water.